title: CFP NATIONAL CHAMPIONSHIP TONIGHT
description:
College Football Live is brought to you live from Indianapolis, IN, the site of the CFP National Championship. The CFB Live crew gets you ready for the biggest game of the season in College Football. We take a look at how we got to this point and final predictions before tonight's National Title game,
